data.description: Embrace waterfront living on the Black Warrior River in this exquisite home, set on a sprawling 2.9-acre oasis. Step inside to an open floor plan bathed in natural light, thanks to a plethora of windows offering uninterrupted river views and rich hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the home. Convenience is at your fingertips with an in-home elevator, connecting all floors. The main level boasts an expansive living area and kitchen. Step out to a spacious screened-in porch or bask in the sun on the open deck, both offering tranquil river views. Upstairs is an entertainer’s dream: a large second living room, additional kitchen, and bedrooms each with private baths. The estate’s prime river location means boating, fishing, and serene nature walks are part of your everyday life.
